sadaqah-silat-rahim\/","url_meta":{"origin":33236,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Family: Best charity given to reconcile family members","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hakim ibn Hizam reported: A man asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhat act of charity is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOne given to an estranged relative.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 15320 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0643\u0650\u064a\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u0650\u0632\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5807,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/02\/charity-family-double-reward\/","url_meta":{"origin":33236,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Family: Charity given to family has two rewards","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman ibn 'Amir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, charity given to the poor has one reward, and charity given to family has two rewards: one for charity and one for upholding family ties.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 658 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34507,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/21\/best-sadaqah-little-available\/","url_meta":{"origin":33236,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Best charity is given when little is available","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which charity is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne with little property to give. Begin with your dependents.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1677 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/12\/best-sadaqah-islah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33236,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Best charity is reconciliation, good relations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best act of charity is to reconcile between people.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 13\/32 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\